# .cursorrules
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# cpdeol.com — Cursor Agent Standing Instructions
# Read this ENTIRE file before every action.
# These rules are permanent and override all stylistic defaults.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────


## ARCHITECTURE — read this first

Single layout stack for every route (same shell as the former /portfolio/* pages).

  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
  │  app/layout.tsx — RootLayout                        │
  │  components/layout/GlobalChrome.tsx → Navbar+Footer │
  │  components/layout/PortfolioShell.tsx               │
  │    → sub-nav pills (Home, About, Services, …)       │
  │    → white card wrapper                             │
  │  {children} — page content                         │
  └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

  Top nav / footer:   components/layout/Navbar.tsx, Footer.tsx
  Sub-nav + card:     components/layout/PortfolioShell.tsx
  Homepage sections:  components/home/*.tsx (no Navbar/Footer there)

  Legacy (unused on render): components/home/Navbar.tsx, Footer.tsx


## 1. FROZEN FILES

Never modify these without the prompt explicitly naming them.
If a required change touches a frozen file, STOP and ask the user.

  Layout (frozen):
  - app/layout.tsx                         ← ONE export default only (RootLayout)
  - components/layout/GlobalChrome.tsx
  - components/layout/PortfolioShell.tsx
  - components/layout/Navbar.tsx
  - components/layout/Footer.tsx

  Legacy homepage chrome (avoid unless migrating away):
  - components/home/Navbar.tsx
  - components/home/Footer.tsx

  Design system (frozen):
  - design-system.ts
  - styles/tailwind.css

  Animation library — NEVER auto-import, opt-in only:
  - components/magicui/animated-gradient-text.tsx
  - components/magicui/blur-fade.tsx
  - components/magicui/marquee.tsx
  - components/magicui/number-ticker.tsx
  - components/magicui/shimmer-button.tsx

  Tests (frozen):
  - playwright.config.ts
  - vitest.config.ts
  - vitest.setup.ts
  - e2e/*


## 2. DESIGN SYSTEM — import tokens, never hardcode

  ✅ DO:   import { DS } from '@/design-system'
           className={DS.card.default}
           className={DS.pills.purple}

  ❌ DON'T: hardcode hex: className="bg-[#EEEDFE] text-[#534AB7]"
  ❌ DON'T: inline styles: style={{ color: '#534AB7' }}
  ❌ DON'T: Tailwind color names: className="bg-purple-100 text-purple-700"

  If a token doesn't exist in design-system.ts, add it there first.
  Never hardcode inline.


## 3. SCOPE — only touch what the prompt names

  ✅ Only edit files listed under "Files to edit" in the prompt
  ❌ Do not clean up, improve, or refactor surrounding code
  ❌ Do not rename variables or reorganize imports
  ❌ Do not reorder or add sections in app/page.tsx unless told to
  ❌ Do not change component prop interfaces unless required by the task


## 4. STYLE — never change without explicit instruction

  - Border radius: use existing Tailwind classes only
  - Font sizes: use DS.text tokens — do not introduce new sizes
  - Spacing: do not adjust padding/margin/gap unless layout is mentioned
  - Animations: never add transitions, keyframes, or motion effects
    unless explicitly requested — never auto-import from magicui/
  - No gradients, shadows, blobs, or background images unless asked
  - No dark: variants unless explicitly asked


## 5. COPY — text content is sacred

  - Never rephrase, rewrite, shorten, or "improve" copy
  - Never change headlines, descriptions, or button labels unless
    the prompt provides the exact replacement text
  - Numbers in ProofMetrics.tsx (60%, 4→1, 83%) are placeholders —
    do not change unless new values are given


## 6. CONTENT DATA — one source of truth

  Landing page content: components/lp-items.tsx
  Do not create a second content file. Do not duplicate content.


## 7. BEFORE COMMITTING — check every time

  - [ ] pnpm build passes, zero TypeScript errors
  - [ ] pnpm lint passes
  - [ ] app/layout.tsx has exactly ONE export default (RootLayout); PortfolioShell wraps page content
  - [ ] No hardcoded hex colors introduced
  - [ ] No frozen files modified (unless explicitly permitted in prompt)
  - [ ] Only files named in the prompt were changed
  - [ ] No magicui components auto-imported


## 8. PROMPT TEMPLATE — use this for every task

  ## Task
  [Exact change — be specific]

  ## Zone
  [ ] Homepage ("/")  →  components/home/* only
  [ ] All routes      →  components/layout/* only
  [ ] Both            →  list files explicitly

  ## Files to edit
  - components/[path]/[Component].tsx ONLY

  ## Do NOT touch
  - [list frozen files relevant to this task]
  - Any styling, layout, or spacing not mentioned above
  - Any copy not provided below

  ## New content (if applicable)
  [Exact replacement text — do not leave to interpretation]

  ## Definition of done
  [One sentence describing the expected result]
